# 🤖 Custom OpenAI Agent

This project is a **custom OpenAI-powered chatbot agent** built with Python and deployed on **Hugging Face Spaces**.  
It demonstrates integration of OpenAI’s API with **Gradio** for a simple interactive UI.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo
[Hugging Face Space](https://huggingface.co/spaces/Mansoor-7429/openai-agent)  
⚠️ *Note: Requires a valid OpenAI API key with billing enabled.*

---

## 📂 Repository
👉 [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/Mansoor-7429/openai-agent)

---

## ⚠️ Important Notice
This project has been successfully built and deployed.  
However, due to OpenAI’s usage policy, it **requires an API key with billing enabled**.  

If you encounter the following error:
openai.RateLimitError: insufficient_quota
it means the API key used has no credits available.

---

## 🛠️ Setup Instructions

git clone https://github.com/Mansoor-7429/openai-agent.git
cd openai-agent

Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

Add your OpenAI API Key

Create a file named .env in the project root:
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

python app.py
You should see a Gradio interface running at:

cpp
Copy code
http://127.0.0.1:7860
📦 Technologies Used
Python

OpenAI API

Gradio (UI)

Hugging Face Spaces

GitHub

Notes
The app is fully functional.
Billing is required on the OpenAI API key to test it.
Hugging Face Space may show an error without a valid API key.
